results.title: Ultimate Spider-Man (2000) #105
results.description:
"THE CLONE SAGA: EPILOGUE" 
Young Peter Parker must pick up the pieces of his life and face a series of terrifying questions: Will Aunt May survive her heart attack? What plans does Nick Fury have for Gwen Stacy? Is Peter being drawn back to MJ, or will he stay with Kitty Pryde? What about the mysterious Spider Woman? The answers will shock you. 
32 PGS./Rated A ...$2.99

items.name: Ultimate Spider-Man Vol. 17: Clone Saga (Trade Paperback)

results.title: Ultimate Spider-Man (2000) #106
results.description:
If you thought Peter would get some time off after the soul-shattering changes that came at the end of "Clone Saga," think again! Things keep heating up, as Ultimate Daredevil attempts to enlist Spider-Man in a crusade to bring down the Kingpin-permanently. But with his Aunt's life hanging by a thread and his serious girl problems...not to mention the new student at Midtown High...crime-busting may be the last thing on young Mr. Parker's mind. So what happens when the rest of Daredevil's new super-team shows up? Learn who stands with Peter-and who stands against him! 
32 PGS. (each)/Rated A ...$2.99
